	<font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size=3 color="black"><B>
	News for 
	010999<P>
        </B></FONT>
	</CENTER

	We are suspending our regular news coverage to bring you this breaking
exclusive  news item.  We will return to our regular format on Monday.
<!-- Begin Day --> 
